### Quran API smoke (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client)
### Set @base to your API origin (no trailing slash)

@base = http://localhost:8787

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### All surahs
GET {{base}}/surahs

### Al-Fatihah
GET {{base}}/surah/1

### Invalid id
GET {{base}}/surah/999

### Search — empty
GET {{base}}/search?q=

### Search — match
GET {{base}}/search?q=mercy&limit=10

### Search — invalid limit (should still 200, default limit)
GET {{base}}/search?q=god&limit=nan
